1) Feature ideas for the diary

- Add / edit / delete entries (timestamped).

- Tags and mood (so you can filter and analyze).

- Search by text, date range, tag, or mood.

- Simple analytics: entries per month, mood-distribution.

- Export selected entries to a CSV or plain-text file.

- Backup and restore (copy CSV).

- Optional password protection (stores a salted hash in a small config file).
